{"tid":2325538,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"女團前一姐暗搭諧星　男方爆曾拉皮條拐「未成年少女」賣淫","createTime":"2020-12-14T15:55:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-14T17:08:17.000Z","uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"974d2917e4da09f9ac989b07015d0612f7dff1d7","tid":2325538,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T15:55:01.000Z","msg":"日本人氣女團AKB48的前一姐指原莉乃，28歲的她在去年離隊後，憑優異的談吐轉戰主持界成功，過去一年在疫情之下卻仍賺逾2億日圓(約新台幣5394萬元)，工作運人氣滿檔。近日，指原莉乃被爆疑與多次合作的29歲的人氣諧星兼近大樹熱戀，有電視台員工指兩人關係不單純，多次合作演出節目互動曖昧。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/12/14/2935498-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F12%2F14%2F2935498-PH.jpg&h=635c9df8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲指原莉乃去年離開AKB48後轉戰主持有成。（圖／翻攝自指原莉乃IG）<br />\n<br />\n近日首屈一指爆料雜誌《週刊文春》更不眠不休派狗仔隊，在指原莉乃的住宅香閨外日夜守候，希望能早日捕捉到兩人幽會的鐵證。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/12/14/2935499-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F12%2F14%2F2935499-PH.jpg&h=a2d24238&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲指原莉乃指（右二）與諧星兼近大樹（左二）走很近。（圖／翻攝自兼近大樹IG）<br />\n<br />\n兼近大樹是搞笑二人組EXIT成員，雖然近期知名度飆升，還在上個月受封GQ年度男士頒獎。被形容為諧星界中首席型男，不過他的負面新聞不少，且作風高調大膽，去年兼近大樹與辣模木村有希於節目上被撮合成一對，當場在節目擁吻令來賓們譁然。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/12/14/2935500-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F12%2F14%2F2935500-PH.jpg&h=99a09fa9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲兼近大樹堪稱是諧星界的首席型男。（圖／翻攝自兼近大樹IG）<br />\n<br />\n他還曾被日本週刊爆料在未成年19歲入行前曾在札幌當「拉皮條」，還安排未成年少女賣淫，2011年遭警方拘捕，隔年又曾因闖入一名牛郎住所竊取財物2度被捕。未走紅時他又曾演出成人節目，為奪得100萬日圓獎金，挑戰一邊唱卡拉OK，一邊被AV女優隔著布幕打手槍，形象相當不佳。"},{"pid":"3e4a6f59bdc67485cf154400d4e841e388c3f944","tid":2325538,"uid":256952,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T15:57:59.000Z","msg":"不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"453c0bb57cc2c5499df03f069a4d939c87396340","tid":2325538,"uid":2545,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T15:58:26.000Z","msg":"未走紅時他又曾演出成人節目，為奪得100萬日圓獎金，挑戰一邊唱卡拉OK，一邊被AV女優隔著布幕打手槍，形象相當不佳。<br />\n<br />\n想睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dda61c1153ed63010cc00247992b06fff542f19b","tid":2325538,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3e4a6f59bdc67485cf154400d4e841e388c3f944","tid":2325538,"uid":256952,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T15:57:59.000Z","msg":"不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T16:05:39.000Z","msg":"八婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6de8d1b9176b5c8d5b78b44f3d69767dd8df8ec4","tid":2325538,"uid":87394,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T16:42:41.000Z","msg":"諧星洗鬼形象咩<br />\n衰過先有野可以自嘲做效果"},{"pid":"9cb15b89019d9a3c0c5c9946f18f16551cc45172","tid":2325538,"uid":46435,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T16:59:57.000Z","msg":"支持為民除害..🙏🏻"},{"pid":"57fc7d6f5edd10d28923ae881898e969d73b4c7f","tid":2325538,"uid":294121,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T17:08:17.000Z","msg":"勁啦AKB一姐做埋媽媽桑<br />\n成堆48同46系大把女揀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}